{"tid":1196541,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"麻煩警察先生們入入黎","createTime":"2019-06-09T20:49:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-09T21:45:51.000Z","uid":243854,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"51fe2583bb1676d27a7cb9f21d90b4374002badb","tid":1196541,"uid":243854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T20:49:32.000Z","msg":"你哋快撚啲死撚晒去啦屌你老母畜牲<br />\n頭先我同朋友喺被圍位上面天橋睇咩事<br />\n落去個位有警犬守住，天橋另一邊馬路下有警犬唔知收工定準備緊<br />\n跟住等緊果班警犬就無啦啦成班畜牲咁吠(有巴打經過)<br />\n我就拎部電話出嚟，影都未撚柒影，班畜牲就吠撚到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過最撚好笑係，班警犬趕我哋去封路位走，俾另一隻警犬叫咪住<br />\n結果我哋俾班警察趕走時，有巴打行慢啲又俾成班狗圍撚住<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />屌你老母，有雞髀俾你班畜牲食咩<br />\n仲有呀，你啲死垃圾講咩失敗者，你老母生你出嚟，無讀過書呢啲戇鳩嘢<br />\n有無用腦諗過其實講緊自己，呢樣心理上叫自卑，你班垃圾都知自己讀書少，老母生你無撚用呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n最後，我只能夠講句抱歉，無能力一拳打柒一隻警犬，只能拉個朋友走快啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n屌你老母送中通過，我就做紅衛兵，到時你班畜牲=公安咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家走到另一條天橋又有成班警犬上黎趕人走<br />\n屌你老母死全家啦警犬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98361dac85a13b2a99ca712f9fdb3c44873eb139","tid":1196541,"uid":243854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T21:01:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9V9kzBM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9V9kzBM.jpg&h=a0b31385&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L3VG3u8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL3VG3u8.jpg&h=c7ac570c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n948Ju9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn948Ju9.jpg&h=bebc7731&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c4becd64f273f0c8fbc3ac9f6071bf3ad3829ee7","tid":1196541,"uid":243854,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T21:02:01.000Z","msg":"等緊=喺地下準備緊班畜牲"},{"pid":"30e15021ff82bbbabdbbe910a053a60c2bf76085","tid":1196541,"uid":243854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-09T21:45:51.000Z","msg":"屌你老母，邊隻警犬畀負評<br />\nBTW 今日俾警犬侮辱無能力反擊，希望12號大家一齊出嚟"}]}